ACE Hardware Survey

Hey, yeah I finally got around to trying that pasta recipe you sent me last month. It was really good! I added some roasted bell peppers and it turned out fantastic. Let me know if you have any other good ones. Work has been crazy busy lately, but things are starting to slow down a bit. Hope you guys are doing well. We should catch up properly soon. I'm thinking of planning a small get-together at the park next weekend if the weather holds up. Just something casual. I'll bring some snacks and that lemonade you liked. Let me know if you're free. Or maybe we can finally catch that movie everyone is talking about. Anyway, no pressure, just wanted to say hi and see how you were doing. Hope to see you soon.

